# Claude skills and scripts are now in a private submodule (.claude/commands/)
# No individual file ignores needed — the submodule handles everything

# Deployment scripts (local only — contain tokens + SAS URLs)
scripts/Deployment/

# Migration tooling (local only, vorerst) — cross-tenant storage/cert migration scripts
scripts/Migration/

# Infra: tracked. The Bicep templates carry no credentials — every secret is a
# @secure() parameter with an empty default, injected at deploy time, and image
# pull runs on managed identity. Keep it that way: never commit a resolved secret
# value or a *.parameters.json holding one.
infra/*.parameters.json

